msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Ayoguḷavagga "
msgstr "3. The Iron Ball "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Paṭhamaphalasutta "
msgstr "25. Fruits (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.285, sc1
msgctxt "sn51.25:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, iddhipādā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four bases of psychic power. "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe … "
msgstr "energy … "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.5"
msgid "cittasamādhi … "
msgstr "mental development … "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—"
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.7"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro iddhipādā. "
msgstr "These are the four bases of psychic power. "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.8"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā bhikkhunā dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—"
msgstr "Because of developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power, one of two results can be expected: "

msgctxt "sn51.25:1.9"
msgid "diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā”ti. "
msgstr "enlightenment in the present life, or if there’s something left over, non-return.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.25:1.10"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
